
Inverness Ridge Stables is a top hunter, jumper, equitation, sales, and show barn located in Davis, CA just a few minutes from Downtown Davis and the UC Davis Campus and 20 minutes from downtown Sacramento. Trainer Molly Brocks approach with her students is fresh and open. She is friendly, smart, and has a strong work ethic. She welcomes all levels of students, from beginners of all ages, to hunter jumper competitors competing on the A circuit.  She offers lesson and training programs tailored to fit the needs and ability of each individual horses horse and rider.

